title: 33: The Best of 2018 Episode
itunes:title: The Best of 2018 Episode
description: It’s the end of the year, and what a year it's been at Hungry Girl! We debuted the “Hungry Girl Chew the Right Thing!” podcast, and thanks to all of you, it’s a BIG HIT! In this BEST OF 2018 episode, Lisa shares with you the best healthy HACKS, SWAPS, CHEW & TELL, and LISA LOVES IT segments from the year! So start the fireplace, and grab a cup of hot cocoa as we look back at the year that was! Happy CHEW Year from Hungry Girl! [www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast](www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast)
